thread.title: BRIEF-Etsy Reports Q4 Revenue $136.3 Million, Up 23.6%

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Etsy Reports Q4 Revenue $136.3 Million, Up 23.6%
text:
Feb 27 (Reuters) - Etsy Inc:
* Q4 REVENUE $136.3 MILLION * ‍TOTAL REVENUE WAS $136.3 MILLION IN Q4 OF 2017, UP 23.6% YEAR-OVER-YEAR​
* ‍GMS WAS $1.0 BILLION IN Q4 OF 2017, UP 17.8% COMPARED WITH 16.7% IN Q4 OF 2016​
* SAYS ‍TOTAL REVENUE WAS $136.3 MILLION IN Q4 OF 2017, UP 23.6% YEAR-OVER-YEAR​
* SEES 2018 ‍REVENUE YEAR-OVER-YEAR GROWTH OF 21% -23%​
* SEES FY18 ‍GMS YEAR-OVER-YEAR GROWTH 14-16%​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
